IF EXISTS ( SELECT * FROM sys.external_tables WHERE object_id = OBJECT_ID('dbo.D_STBillZone') )
    DROP EXTERNAL TABLE dbo.D_STBillZone
GO

CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE dbo.D_STBillZone (
    [lms_billzone_id] int,
    [lms_billzone_description] nvarchar(4000),
    [lms_billzone_zonemasterid] int,
    [lms_billzone_countryid] int


	)
	WITH (
	LOCATION = 'Structured Data/OPS/stbillzone.parquet',
	DATA_SOURCE = [synapse_citylogisticsstorage_dfs_core_windows_net],
	FILE_FORMAT = [SynapseParquetFormat]
	)
GO


SELECT TOP 100 * FROM dbo.D_STBillZone 
GO
